  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cannon fire is a game all about blowing your friends' ship to pieces, in Multiplayer or Split-Screen mode for the best experience. The game uses a low poly artistic style to capture an almost Caribbean setting. The game has different types of ships witch all vary in size, damage, health, and speed. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ship types currently in the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Galion<br></li><li>Warship<br></li><li>RPG jetski</li></ul></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer now available!</h2>",
